<entry code="DQC.US.0195.10625" level="error">
 <message filing_url="http://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1842939/000095017025087485/xage-20241231.htm" severity="error" effectiveDate="2025-04-15" cid="2955448168720">[DQC.US.0195.10625] us-gaap:TreasuryStockSharesRetired has a value of 3,845,337 and has been used with the common stock member on the StatementEquityComponentsAxis. This element should not have a value when used with the common stock Member as us-gaap:TreasuryStockSharesRetired should not impact common stock. 

The Statement of Changes in Equity implies treasury stock is excluded from the opening balance of shares as the opening balance uses a shares outstanding concept. The element TreasuryStockSharesRetired that was used in the roll-forward cannot reduce the shares outstanding. If the roll-forward of shares is based on shares issued the element TreasuryStockSharesRetired can be used but the  opening balance share element should be changed to SharesIssued or CommonStockSharesIssued.

The properties of this us-gaap:TreasuryStockSharesRetired fact are:
Period :2024-01-01 to 2024-12-31
Dimensions : us-gaap:StatementEquityComponentsAxis=us-gaap:CommonStockMember
Unit : shares
Rule Element Id:10625
Rule version: 30.0.0RC1 - xage-20241231.htm 4329</message>
